About Enterprise Partnership & Solutions Team
We are a technology company operating a range of content platforms that inform, educate, entertain and inspire people across languages, cultures and geographies. Dedicated to building global platforms of creation and interaction, the company now has a portfolio of applications available in over 150 markets and 75 languages. It includes Toutiao, Helo, TikTok, Douyin, News Republic, Vigo, TopBuzz and FaceU, etc. The success of our products is attributed to the usage of cutting-edge machine learning technologies such as NLP, ML, CV, Data Mining, Speech&Audio, etc. Enterprise Partnership & Solutions team enables our enterprise customers a successful digital transformation with our advanced machine learning technologies. We are looking for talented individuals to join us - people who want to inspire creativity and co-create the future with us. Successful candidates must be able to commit to the following internship cycle below: -
1. Off-cycle... Internship - 02 Aug to 17 Dec (20 weeks)
Please state your availability clearly in the comments section (Start date, End date). Responsibilities
1. Provide artificial intelligence solutions for customers;
2. Understand business needs and goals, and turn business problems into machine learning problems;
3. Conduct cutting-edge research in machine learning algorithms, and apply the technology to different business scenarios.
1. Undergraduate or Postgraduate with a background in Computer Science, Computer Engineering, Information Systems or a related technical discipline;
2. Proficient coding skills and strong algorithm & data structure basis;
3. Familiar with machine learning and/or NLP and/or data mining skills, preferably experienced in developing recommendation system, advertisement calculation, search engine;
4. Great problem analysis and solving skills, passionate about solving challenges;
5. Passionate about technology, good at communication and teamwork. Application deadline: 15 April 2021
1. Applications will be reviewed on a rolling basis and we encourage you to apply early;
2. Interview starts from February 2021
